Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.08,0:24:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的劳拉  不要惊慌  我是汤姆\N{\rEnglish}Dear Lara, don't panic. It's Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.60,0:24:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被困在一只猫的身体里了\N{\rEnglish}I seem to be trapped in the body of a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.04,0:24:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是开玩笑\N{\rEnglish}This is not a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.28,0:25:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你亲爱的老公  汤姆\N{\rEnglish}Your loving husband, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.48,0:25:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  这样不行\N{\rEnglish}Okay, that didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.08,0:25:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  对于一只猫来说已经不错了\N{\rEnglish}Although, not bad for a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.28,0:25:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讽刺的是  我现在真想玩鼠标\N{\rEnglish}Ironically, I could really use a mouse right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.92,0:25:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  爸爸什么时候回家\N{\rEnglish}Mommy, when is Daddy gonna come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.56,0:25:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一醒过来  就会回来\N{\rEnglish}Just as soon as he wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.12,0:25:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们应该用一个大闹钟闹醒他\N{\rEnglish}They should use a really big alarm clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.52,0:25:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将来会成为一个好医生的\N{\rEnglish}You'd be a great doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.92,0:25:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么  猫咪\N{\rEnglish}What do you want, kitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.00,0:26:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱夹  加上  身份证  等于\N{\rEnglish}Money clip, plus license equals...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.64,0:26:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被困在猫里\N{\rEnglish}I'm stuck in a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.96,0:26:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它想要和我们一起玩\N{\rEnglish}He wants to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.64,0:26:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  猫咪  我们要睡了\N{\rEnglish}Well, sorry, kitty. It is bedtime in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.44,0:26:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们明天可以一起玩\N{\rEnglish}But we can play tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.20,0:26:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天\N{\rEnglish}Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.00,0:26:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.76,0:26:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚才说到哪儿了\N{\rEnglish}Where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.96,0:28:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我在猫的身体里\N{\rEnglish}If I'm in a cat's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.32,0:28:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只猫在我身体里吗\N{\rEnglish}is a cat in my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.80,0:28:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都讨厌这块地毯\N{\rEnglish}I always hated that rug.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.04,0:28:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个苏格兰威士忌后劲真不赖\N{\rEnglish}This is good scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.40,0:29:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚很难熬\N{\rEnglish}Rough night?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.48,0:29:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  我只是在沉思\N{\rEnglish}No. I was just contemplating
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.44,0:29:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何以猫的身体度过余生\N{\rEnglish}the rest of my life as a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.56,0:29:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.40,0:29:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪\N{\rEnglish}Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.24,0:29:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你饿了吗\N{\rEnglish}Who's hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.52,0:29:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦\N{\rEnglish}Yum yum.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.68,0:29:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了就饱了\N{\rEnglish}Looks like a cat already ate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.88,0:29:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你有个好胃口\N{\rEnglish}Bon appetit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.64,0:29:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法国人  他们就会卖这些东西\N{\rEnglish}French. That'll sell this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.88,0:29:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\rEnglish}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.44,0:29:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的猫厕所\N{\rEnglish}There's your litter box.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.72,0:29:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我有那块地毯了\N{\rEnglish}No, thank you, I have the rug.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.55,0:30:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnSTKaiti\fs18}留给爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.60,0:30:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时有事才没来的\N{\rEnglish}I had a really good excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.60,0:30:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在她泪闸要开了\N{\rEnglish}Here come the floodgates.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.40,0:30:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能觉得我为了一块蛋糕就哭  好像疯了\N{\rEnglish}You probably think I'm crazy crying over a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.04,0:30:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是为了你的丈夫还在医院里昏迷\N{\rEnglish}Or that your husband's in the hospital in a coma.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.60,0:30:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会醒过来的\N{\rEnglish}He's gonna wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.28,0:30:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧\N{\rEnglish}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.96,0:30:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要去找那个叫珀金斯的\N{\rEnglish}Oh, I really gotta find that Perkins guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.92,0:30:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿醉中\N{\rEnglish}Hangover!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.60,0:30:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  猫咪\N{\rEnglish}Hello, kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.44,0:30:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们该叫你什么名字\N{\rEnglish}What should we call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.32,0:30:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的名字吗  毛绒裤先生\N{\rEnglish}Is that your name? Mister Fuzzypants?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.96,0:30:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨的因果报应\N{\rEnglish}I hate karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.40,0:30:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我得到过最棒的礼物\N{\rEnglish}You're the best gift I ever got.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.00,0:30:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  太贴心了\N{\rEnglish}No, too sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.56,0:30:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不好笑\N{\rEnglish}That wasn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.12,0:31:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们俩在笑什么\N{\rEnglish}What are you two laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.72,0:31:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没觉得好笑\N{\rEnglish}I don't think it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.96,0:31:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗  这就是我的观点\N{\rEnglish}See, this is my point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.24,0:31:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不需要增加高度  而是要使用一些策略\N{\rEnglish}We don't need high rises, we need strategic growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.12,0:31:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们说的就是这个意思\N{\rEnglish}And that's what we've all been saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.44,0:31:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在根本不应该讨论这些\N{\rEnglish}We shouldn't even be talking about this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.76,0:31:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们面对的并非危机\N{\rEnglish}This isn't a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.08,0:31:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是机遇\N{\rEnglish}This is an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.12,0:31:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.00,0:31:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么\N{\rEnglish}What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.32,0:31:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃东西的话  去猫食盆里找\N{\rEnglish}If you want food, it's in the bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.25,0:31:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnSTKaiti\fs18}我不是我\N我是人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.88,0:31:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吃果味麦片\N{\rEnglish}Fruity Pebbles
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.04,0:32:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是吃那个\N{\rEnglish}or that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.04,0:32:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就吃果味麦片\N{\rEnglish}Fruity Pebbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.20,0:32:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是猫  我是猫  我是猫  我是猫\N{\rEnglish}Be the cat, be the cat, be the cat, be the cat, be the cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.40,0:32:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很优雅\N{\rEnglish}Graceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.52,0:32:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  你来试试\N{\rEnglish}Yeah? You try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.28,0:32:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功登陆\N{\rEnglish}And, nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.12,0:32:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也打电话给你妈妈了\N{\rEnglish}I called your mom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.24,0:32:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望把大家聚在一起\N{\rEnglish}I just wanted to get everyone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.92,0:32:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道真诱人\N{\rEnglish}Well, it smells great.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.20,0:32:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么吃的\N{\rEnglish}What are you cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.48,0:32:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤全猫\N{\rEnglish}Roast cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.68,0:32:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计它的脑袋刚才摔坏了\N{\rEnglish}Maybe its head got screwed up in the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.80,0:32:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是个酒鬼  不肯吃东西\N{\rEnglish}He's an alcoholic. I can't get him to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.40,0:32:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我却发现装着五十年麦卡伦的\N{\rEnglish}but I found an empty decanter,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.72,0:32:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒瓶空空如也  上面沾满了猫毛\N{\rEnglish}of 50-year-old Macallan with fur all over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.68,0:32:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少它品味还不错\N{\rEnglish}Well, at least he has good taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.40,0:33:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我应该在它的食物里掺点苏格兰威士忌\N{\rEnglish}Maybe I should mix scotch into his food.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.72,0:33:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能用一下爸爸的办公室吗\N{\rEnglish}Can I use Dad's office for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.92,0:33:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  怎么了\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.04,0:33:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看我还能做些什么\N{\rEnglish}I just want to see if I can find anything else
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.76,0:33:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来扭转这整个芝加哥的...\N{\rEnglish}that might help me with this whole Chicago...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.48,0:33:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫可以做核磁共振吗\N{\rEnglish}Do they make MRIs for cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.88,0:33:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指CAT扫描[层状扫描]吗\N{\rEnglish}You mean CAT scans?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.56,0:33:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掉在刀上就好了\N{\rEnglish}I should have landed on the knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.20,0:33:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去办公室了\N{\rEnglish}I'll be in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.40,0:33:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\rEnglish}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.04,0:33:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道\N{\rEnglish}So,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.20,0:33:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在跟爸爸一样了吗\N{\rEnglish}are you like Dad now?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.96,0:33:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么\N{\rEnglish}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.12,0:33:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成为公司的总裁了吗\N{\rEnglish}Are you president of the company?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.16,0:33:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我的工作没变化  只是没有爸爸在了\N{\rEnglish}No, I'm doing the same job, just without Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.68,0:33:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你过会儿能出来吗\N{\rEnglish}Can you come out soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.12,0:33:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以  马上就来\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.76,0:33:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是像极了爸爸\N{\rEnglish}You're so totally like Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.04,0:33:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉\N{\rEnglish}Lara!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.40,0:33:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下可好  "撒旦"过来吃晚饭了\N{\rEnglish}Oh, good! Satan's over for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.36,0:33:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆的事我很抱歉\N{\rEnglish}So sorry about Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.40,0:34:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为他会因为跳伞出事\N{\rEnglish}I always thought it would be skydiving,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.44,0:34:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者他的秘书会带着\N{\rEnglish}or that his secretary would just snap
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.96,0:34:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一支乌兹冲锋枪冲到办公室\N{\rEnglish}and bring an Uzi to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.60,0:34:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还觉得你会因肉毒素过量而死呢\N{\rEnglish}I thought you'd die from a Botox overdose.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.08,0:34:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把狗带来了\N{\rEnglish}Oh, you brought the dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.84,0:34:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  珍妮特\N{\rEnglish}Princess, Jeanette!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.96,0:34:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道汤姆昏迷了吧  你可以休息一个晚上\N{\rEnglish}You know Tom's unconscious, right? You can take the night off.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.92,0:34:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  可总得有人继续干活啊\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, well, someone has to keep things going.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.96,0:34:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永远搞不懂你为什么要为他工作\N{\rEnglish}I never understood why you wanted to work for him anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.52,0:34:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈  你能不和我说话...\N{\rEnglish}Mom, if we could not talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.44,0:34:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝这个可不健康\N{\rEnglish}This isn't healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.12,0:34:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治疗悲伤的心灵鸡汤\N{\rEnglish}Chicken soup for grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.44,0:35:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别追了  走开\N{\rEnglish}Stop it. Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.68,0:35:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下\N{\rEnglish}Heel!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.04,0:35:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能把它们带走吗  它们吓到它了\N{\rEnglish}Can you please take them away? They're really scaring him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.28,0:35:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们对其他动物特别敏感\N{\rEnglish}They have a very strong sense about other animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.88,0:35:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你爸爸从哪里把它弄来的  -怎么了\N{\rEnglish}- Where'd your dad get him? - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.96,0:35:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会是从大街上捡回来的吧\N{\rEnglish}Well, did he just pick him up off the streets?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.08,0:35:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它只是毛有些乱而已\N{\rEnglish}He's just a little messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.88,0:35:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不开心  因为你爸爸快死了\N{\rEnglish}I know you're upset because your dad's dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.28,0:35:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会死的  他只是昏迷\N{\rEnglish}He's not dying. He's just unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.00,0:35:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈说了  你妈妈\N{\rEnglish}My mom says your mom
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.89,0:35:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该客观面对他的情况\N{\rEnglish}should be more realistic about his condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.64,0:35:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  珍妮特  坐下\N{\rEnglish}Princess, Jeanette, heel!
