Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.32,0:35:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O\N{\rEnglish}O
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.56,0:35:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M\N{\rEnglish}M.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.20,0:35:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnSTKaiti\fs18}汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.15,0:35:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆\N{\rEnglish}Tom
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.20,0:35:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦迪逊  大卫  丽贝卡  妮可\N{\rEnglish}Madison, David, Rebecca, Nicole.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.12,0:35:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.40,0:35:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给汤姆留了个位子\N{\rEnglish}I set a place for Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.04,0:35:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是个怪异的习惯\N{\rEnglish}Well, that's a weird habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.27,0:35:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该通常不在家吃晚饭吧\N{\rEnglish}It's not like he's usually here for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.60,0:35:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦迪逊  别在今晚说这些\N{\rEnglish}Madison, not tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.24,0:35:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他在  我也是这么说\N{\rEnglish}I'd say the same thing if he were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.56,0:35:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  所以没有人喜欢你\N{\rEnglish}Yes, that's why nobody likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.08,0:36:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你一直去找乔什总是有原因的\N{\rEnglish}But there's a reason you've been seeing Josh.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.24,0:36:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔什\N{\rEnglish}Josh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.36,0:36:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在可不愿想那事\N{\rEnglish}Oh, I can't even think about that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.08,0:36:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是大好时机  汤姆不可能发现了\N{\rEnglish}Now's the perfect time. It's not like Tom could catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.96,0:36:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁还需要猫砂盆吗\N{\rEnglish}Who needs a litter box?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.44,0:36:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦迪逊  我是一只坏坏猫\N{\rEnglish}Oh, Madison? I've been a bad kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.28,0:36:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...\N{\rEnglish}Hey! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.56,0:36:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来\N{\rEnglish}Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.28,0:36:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉\N{\rEnglish}Sorry, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.80,0:36:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-等等  -怎么了\N{\rEnglish}- Wait. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.32,0:36:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  我还以为我看到了...没事\N{\rEnglish}Nothing, I just thought I saw... Nothing. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.00,0:36:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉  快把那只猫杀了\N{\rEnglish}Lara, that cat needs to be put down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.32,0:36:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你买个新包  麦迪逊\N{\rEnglish}I'll buy you a new bag, Madison.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.64,0:37:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个训猫师  或者猫语者什么的  我不管\N{\rEnglish}Hire a trainer, a cat whisperer, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.40,0:37:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来给你开瓶新的马丁尼酒\N{\rEnglish}Let's get you a new martini.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.52,0:37:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\rEnglish}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.80,0:37:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总得有人说说这空椅子的事吧\N{\rEnglish}Well, someone's gotta talk about the empty chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.64,0:37:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是不是该说段祝酒词\N{\rEnglish}Should we do toasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.84,0:37:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又不是守灵  妈\N{\rEnglish}It's not a wake, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.36,0:37:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是汤姆第一次进医院了\N{\rEnglish}This isn't Tom's first time in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.64,0:37:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得他成立航空公司那会儿吗\N{\rEnglish}Remember when he launched the airline?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.56,0:37:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他总是在打电话  不眠不休\N{\rEnglish}He was always on the phone, never slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.68,0:37:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得你问我什么\N{\rEnglish}You know what you asked me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.00,0:37:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼\N{\rEnglish}Vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.12,0:37:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么爸爸是个吸血鬼\N{\rEnglish}Why is Daddy a vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.00,0:37:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为妈妈把他的血吸干了\N{\rEnglish}Because Mommy sucked all his blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.44,0:37:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他通宵达旦地工作\N{\rEnglish}He'd stay awake all night working out,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.24,0:37:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后有一天  他在跑步机上跑步时就睡着了\N{\rEnglish}and then one day, he just fell asleep on a moving treadmill.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.00,0:37:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在医院呆了一周\N{\rEnglish}He was in the hospital for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.12,0:37:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我最棒的假期\N{\rEnglish}Best vacation I ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.88,0:37:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时我在凌晨四点醒来  发现他在阳台上\N{\rEnglish}I'd wake up and find him on the balcony at 4:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.92,0:37:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆呆地望着他的大厦\N{\rEnglish}just staring at his tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.84,0:37:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得为汤姆说句话\N{\rEnglish}I'll say this for Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.96,0:37:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他从来没有其他女人\N{\rEnglish}There was never another woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.20,0:37:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我在一起时  是航空公司\N{\rEnglish}With me, it was an airline.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.44,0:37:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你在一起时  是摩天大厦\N{\rEnglish}With you, it's a big skyscraper.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.52,0:37:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚听到的话都别当真\N{\rEnglish}Ignore everything you hear tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.12,0:37:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拿我做榜样  丽贝卡\N{\rEnglish}I'm not a role model, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.04,0:37:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经习惯了\N{\rEnglish}You're used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.60,0:37:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说段祝酒词吧\N{\rEnglish}How about that toast?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.44,0:37:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-祝爸爸早日醒过来  -我们想念你\N{\rEnglish}- To Dad. Wake up soon. - We miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.84,0:37:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说你的大厦想念你\N{\rEnglish}Or your tower misses you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.88,0:38:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得好吗\N{\rEnglish}Sleep well?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.36,0:38:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽贝卡·艾莉森·布兰德\N{\rEnglish}Rebecca Alison Brand,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.06,0:38:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的猫把黄页给毁了\N{\rEnglish}your cat destroyed the yellow pages!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.88,0:38:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄页是什么\N{\rEnglish}What's a yellow pages?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.71,0:38:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnSTKaiti\fs18}喵金斯宠物店\N出售宠物\N食物和用品\N猫咪寄放\N行为训练\N咨询
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.48,0:38:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你买的那只猫\N{\rEnglish}That cat you got,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.92,0:38:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸亏你这会儿在医院里\N{\rEnglish}he's lucky you're in here
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.96,0:38:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你已经把它给宰了\N{\rEnglish}or you'd have killed him by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.72,0:38:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个计划可以击败芝加哥\N{\rEnglish}I got a plan to beat Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.08,0:38:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等董事会接受这个计划了\N{\rEnglish}I just need to sell it to the Board.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.24,0:38:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你醒过来  我们可能已经成为第一名了\N{\rEnglish}When you wake up, we might be number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.00,0:38:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会尽力的\N{\rEnglish}We're doing the best that we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.28,0:38:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  非常感谢\N{\rEnglish}Okay. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.68,0:39:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这儿干什么\N{\rEnglish}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.00,0:39:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手腕扭了  所以才拉不住你爸爸\N{\rEnglish}Sprained my wrist. That's why I couldn't hold on to your Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.36,0:39:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来找我爸的神经科医生看手腕\N{\rEnglish}You're seeing my Dad's neurologist about your wrist?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.36,0:39:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,董事会需要他最新的身体状况\N{\rEnglish}The Board needs updates on his status.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.60,0:39:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那问我啊\N{\rEnglish}So ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.84,0:39:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会从悲痛丧父的人那里听取医疗建议的\N{\rEnglish}We're not going to take medical advice from the grieving son.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.24,0:39:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是公司的巨大转型\N{\rEnglish}It's a massive transition for the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.56,0:39:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么转型\N{\rEnglish}What transition?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.76,0:39:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办公室的大日子  祝你与董事会沟通顺利\N{\rEnglish}Big day at the office. Good luck with the Board.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.60,0:39:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们差了那么多\N{\rEnglish}We're losing by that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.96,0:39:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多20米  我们就第一了\N{\rEnglish}We get 70 feet, we're number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.48,0:39:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在的结构不能支撑再多一层\N{\rEnglish}Now, our structure can't support another floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.64,0:39:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜我们也不能\N{\rEnglish}and unfortunately we can't
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.92,0:39:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷运一个大铁锤进芝加哥\N{\rEnglish}just smuggle a wrecking ball into Chicago,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.08,0:39:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们需要减重\N{\rEnglish}so we need to shed weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.72,0:39:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为我们要建高一些\N{\rEnglish}I thought we were making it taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.44,0:39:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们拆掉一层\N{\rEnglish}We lose one floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.36,0:39:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能换来这个\N{\rEnglish}it buys us this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.64,0:39:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会塌的\N{\rEnglish}That's gonna collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.96,0:39:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用钛合金就不会\N{\rEnglish}Not if we use titanium.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.16,0:39:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不用黄金呢\N{\rEnglish}Why don't we just build it out of gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.48,0:39:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它和钢一样硬  但重量只有一半\N{\rEnglish}It's as strong as steel and half the weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.44,0:39:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在解决什么问题\N{\rEnglish}I don't know what problem you're trying to solve here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.84,0:39:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思\N{\rEnglish}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.96,0:39:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是曼哈顿的核心地产\N{\rEnglish}This is a stack of prime real estate in Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.32,0:39:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个金字塔攀爬顶可收不了租金\N{\rEnglish}We can't charge rent on a jungle gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.80,0:39:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲建造北半球最高的楼\N{\rEnglish}My father didn't build the tallest skyscraper
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.56,0:39:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了一点点租金\N{\rEnglish}in the Northern Hemisphere for a little rent money.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.76,0:39:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不是最高的楼\N{\rEnglish}It's not the tallest skyscraper.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.32,0:39:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你搞砸了\N{\rEnglish}Because you screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.28,0:40:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  如果汤姆在这里\N{\rEnglish}Look. If Tom were here,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.65,0:40:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他绝对会这么做\N{\rEnglish}you know this is exactly what he would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.24,0:40:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很钦佩你如此尊重你父亲的想法  大卫\N{\rEnglish}I appreciate that you want to honor your father, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.32,0:40:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得注意账目\N{\rEnglish}We need to watch the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.56,0:40:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司不能总是把钱花在汤姆的玩乐项目上\N{\rEnglish}Our company can't keep diverting funds into Tom's pet projects.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.28,0:40:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他的公司\N{\rEnglish}It's his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.56,0:40:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  大卫\N{\rEnglish}Thank you, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.16,0:40:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还没死\N{\rEnglish}He's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.40,0:40:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想试试吗\N{\rEnglish}You wanna try?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.52,0:40:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想试试吗\N{\rEnglish}You wanna try?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.60,0:40:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天救救我吧\N{\rEnglish}Lord help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.60,0:40:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来试试  包包不是垃圾箱\N{\rEnglish}Okay, let's try "A purse is not a litter box."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.68,0:40:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包包不是垃圾箱\N{\rEnglish}A purse is not a litter box.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.92,0:40:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛绒裤先生是她父亲给她的最后一样东西\N{\rEnglish}Mr. Fuzzypants was the last thing her father gave her,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.36,0:40:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她很粘着它\N{\rEnglish}so she's really latched on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.04,0:40:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它想博得注意  看得出来\N{\rEnglish}Mmm. He wants attention, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.04,0:40:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这是我们的女儿  丽贝卡  -你好\N{\rEnglish}- This is our daughter, Rebecca. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.32,0:40:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得把我说的每句话都讲给他们听\N{\rEnglish}You are going to tell them every word I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.16,0:41:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔得漂亮  不错\N{\rEnglish}Good move. Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.64,0:41:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒来试试\N{\rEnglish}You try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.88,0:41:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸从我的店里买了这只猫  你知道吗\N{\rEnglish}Your dad bought this cat at my store. Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.92,0:41:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁在乎  帮我翻译\N{\rEnglish}Who cares? Just translate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.56,0:41:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得他说\N{\rEnglish}I remember, he said
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.53,0:41:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想把你说想要的给到你\N{\rEnglish}he wanted you to have exactly what you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.84,0:41:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫痴  我不是让你过来无视我的\N{\rEnglish}Hey, cat freak, I didn't call you down here to ignore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.52,0:41:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我们单独待会儿吗\N{\rEnglish}Could we have a moment of privacy, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.64,0:41:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和猫\N{\rEnglish}You and the cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.88,0:41:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是的  -好吧\N{\rEnglish}- Yeah. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.64,0:41:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没时间玩游戏了  布兰德先生\N{\rEnglish}You don't have time for games, Mr. Brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.96,0:41:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们我是谁\N{\rEnglish}Tell them who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.52,0:41:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你的新闻发布人\N{\rEnglish}I'm not your press agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.88,0:41:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个猫语者\N{\rEnglish}Well, you're a cat whisperer,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.08,0:41:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挺能肯定我还是只猫\N{\rEnglish}and I'm pretty sure I'm still a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.92,0:41:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没问过自己\N{\rEnglish}Have you asked yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.08,0:41:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么落到这个地步的\N{\rEnglish}how you got into this position?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.72,0:41:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试过上网搜  但你知道\N{\rEnglish}I tried googling it, but you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.96,0:41:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有给猫爪子用的键盘\N{\rEnglish}they don't make keyboards for paws!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.08,0:41:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你像个野兽一样  快把你家人逼疯了\N{\rEnglish}You're acting like a beast and you're driving your family crazy.
