Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.60,0:51:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\rEnglish}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.24,0:51:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\rEnglish}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.23,0:51:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnSTKaiti\fs18}爱你的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.00,0:51:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个傻瓜\N{\rEnglish}I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.48,0:51:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该当一位更好的爸爸\N{\rEnglish}I should have been a better dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.16,0:51:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈说你现在需要人陪\N{\rEnglish}My mom said you needed company right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.04,0:51:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就自告奋勇来了\N{\rEnglish}so I'm volunteering my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.08,0:51:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在有点想一个人待着\N{\rEnglish}I kind of wanna be alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.88,0:51:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该去洗一下脸\N{\rEnglish}You should go wash your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.60,0:51:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭鼻子真的不适合你的肤色\N{\rEnglish}Crying really doesn't work with your complexion.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.44,0:51:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是一团糟\N{\rEnglish}She's a wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.20,0:52:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的蠢猫拿了我的\N{\rEnglish}Your stupid cat took my...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.24,0:52:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要分享这个\N{\rEnglish}Why would you share this?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.04,0:52:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想给男孩子们看看\N{\rEnglish}I wanted to show some boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.04,0:52:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们看见你这么脆弱\N{\rEnglish}If they see you when you're vulnerable,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.72,0:52:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会想要照顾你以及\N{\rEnglish}they'll wanna take care of you and...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.88,0:52:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把这照片发给了半个班的人看\N{\rEnglish}You sent this one to half our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.80,0:52:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个玩笑而已\N{\rEnglish}That was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.92,0:52:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗  我爸爸现在在医院里昏迷不醒\N{\rEnglish}You know what, my dad is in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.76,0:52:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你解释给我听这算什么玩笑\N{\rEnglish}Explain the joke to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.28,0:52:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想帮帮忙\N{\rEnglish}I was just trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.08,0:52:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友间就该这么做\N{\rEnglish}That's what friends do.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.48,0:52:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗  我妈妈和你妈妈是朋友\N{\rEnglish}You know what, my mom is friends with your mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.80,0:52:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常看你过来\N{\rEnglish}and I see you over here a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.36,0:52:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但别装了  妮可\N{\rEnglish}but stop pretending, Nicole.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.68,0:52:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是朋友\N{\rEnglish}We're not friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.04,0:52:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我简直无法相信你会这么做\N{\rEnglish}I can't believe you just did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.12,0:52:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  但你为什么会去拿她的手机\N{\rEnglish}Good work, but why did you grab her phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.60,0:52:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是你爸爸\N{\rEnglish}Because I'm your daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.40,0:53:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利梵托  中等研磨  苦味与醇度兼具\N{\rEnglish}Livanto, round and balanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.60,0:53:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在不能玩  毛绒裤先生\N{\rEnglish}I can't play, Mr. Fuzzypants.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.84,0:53:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是正确答案\N{\rEnglish}That was the right answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.28,0:53:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只有这样才能重新变成人\N{\rEnglish}If this is what it takes to become human,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.84,0:53:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要成为这世上最好的猫\N{\rEnglish}I will be the best cat that ever lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.00,0:54:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你带了点会让你醒来的东西\N{\rEnglish}Hey, I brought something that's gonna wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.80,0:54:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一张参加北半球\N{\rEnglish}An invitation to the grand opening
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.84,0:54:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高避雷针\N{\rEnglish}of the tallest lightning rod
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.40,0:54:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开幕式的邀请函\N{\rEnglish}in the Northern Hemisphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.88,0:54:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怀念跟你分享事情  汤姆\N{\rEnglish}I miss sharing things with you, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.68,0:54:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你得醒过来\N{\rEnglish}That's why you need to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.80,0:54:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会孤身一人去参加这个开幕式的\N{\rEnglish}I'm not going to this thing without a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.73,0:54:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnSTKaiti\fs18}火兰德管理层谣言四起
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.68,0:54:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想出解决办法了吗\N{\rEnglish}Are you figuring this out?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.52,0:54:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再看一下爸爸的那些文件\N{\rEnglish}Hey. I just want another look at Dad's files.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.24,0:54:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.36,0:54:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都还好吗\N{\rEnglish}Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.28,0:54:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们今天早上选定了投资者\N{\rEnglish}They locked up investors this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.48,0:54:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火兰德要在纽交所上市了\N{\rEnglish}FireBrand's going to the New York Stock Exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.60,0:54:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候\N{\rEnglish}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.76,0:54:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会在塔楼开幕的时候宣布\N{\rEnglish}They're announcing it when they open the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.84,0:55:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩完全瞒着我们\N{\rEnglish}Ian totally went behind our back.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.56,0:55:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他联合了本森和施泰因以及董事会的其他成员\N{\rEnglish}He's lined up Benson and Stein and the rest of the Board
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.64,0:55:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,签订了一项秘密交易协定\N{\rEnglish}in a secret deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.48,0:55:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来伊恩已经谋划这个计划好几个月了\N{\rEnglish}Turns out, Ian's been working on this plan for months
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.40,0:55:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一直在等待适当的时机\N{\rEnglish}and was waiting for the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.64,0:55:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆会杀了他们的\N{\rEnglish}Tom would kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.84,0:55:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不在乎\N{\rEnglish}They don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.24,0:55:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有留下什么书面指示吗\N{\rEnglish}Did he leave any directives or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.48,0:55:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有份遗嘱  可他还活着啊\N{\rEnglish}Uh, there's a will, but he's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.20,0:55:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  我知道\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, I know, I know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.16,0:55:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望能有个凭证\N{\rEnglish}I just hope there's something in here
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.80,0:55:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我赢下这场仗\N{\rEnglish}that'll help me fight this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.16,0:55:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死  到处都是我\N{\rEnglish}Damn. I'm everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.68,0:56:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnSTKaiti\fs18}百丽宫大厦  火兰德大楼\N加塔尖  加高楼顶
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.64,0:56:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大卫·布兰德\N{\rEnglish}David Brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.72,0:56:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得给你加薪了\N{\rEnglish}You're gonna need a raise.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.12,0:56:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  还是先给你升个职\N{\rEnglish}But first, let's give you a promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.64,0:56:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大卫正收集资料  打算采取法律手段\N{\rEnglish}David's pulling files from legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.30,0:56:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定会拼尽全力\N{\rEnglish}He's gonna fight this.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.24,0:56:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要我们投入市场  他就无力回天了\N{\rEnglish}As long as we get to market, he can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.28,0:56:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司章程  在哪里\N{\rEnglish}Articles of incorporation. Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.68,0:56:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在汤姆的办公桌抽屉里发现了这个\N{\rEnglish}I did find this in Tom's desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.84,0:56:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把所有的投票股权都留给了大卫\N{\rEnglish}He left all his voting shares to David.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.48,0:57:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审计部门发现这类文件了吗\N{\rEnglish}Did the audit find anything like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.28,0:57:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然没有\N{\rEnglish}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.52,0:57:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大卫知道  他肯定知道\N{\rEnglish}David knows. He has to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.28,0:57:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他知道  我们早就被赶走了\N{\rEnglish}If he knew, we wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.32,0:57:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从未见过汤姆拥抱大卫\N{\rEnglish}I never saw Tom hug David.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.08,0:57:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太喜欢拥抱\N{\rEnglish}I'm not much of a hugger.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.36,0:57:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他让大卫在那个杂物间里办公\N{\rEnglish}He's got him working out of that broom closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.68,0:57:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是忍不住想叫儿童服务中心来\N{\rEnglish}I keep wanting to call Child Services.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.40,0:57:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么\N{\rEnglish}Well then,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.24,0:57:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没见过这个  你呢\N{\rEnglish}I never saw this. Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.88,0:57:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有\N{\rEnglish}Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.96,0:57:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很欣赏你处理棘手问题的方式\N{\rEnglish}We all appreciate the way you've handled this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.97,0:57:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnSTKaiti\fs18}公司章程
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.04,0:57:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果汤姆没挺过来  我们希望你来主持大局\N{\rEnglish}If Tom doesn't pull through, we want you to take the helm.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.88,0:57:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  谢谢\N{\rEnglish}Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.52,0:57:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnSTKaiti\fs18}坚持住  宝贝儿
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.96,0:57:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-坚持住  -好\N{\rEnglish}- Hang in there. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.20,0:58:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈\N{\rEnglish}Hey, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.36,0:59:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把市值数十亿的公司交给你\N{\rEnglish}I hand you the keys to a multi-billion dollar company
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.40,0:59:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却打电话给你妈\N{\rEnglish}and you call your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.48,0:59:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们离婚时拿到的文件都还留着吗\N{\rEnglish}Do you still have the files from the divorce?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.56,0:59:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聪明\N{\rEnglish}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.20,0:59:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  珍妮特  闭嘴\N{\rEnglish}Princess, Jeanette, shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.60,0:59:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司头十年的所有档案全在这里了\N{\rEnglish}All of the company records for the first 10 years are in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.96,0:59:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该扔掉的\N{\rEnglish}Should probably get rid of this stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.71,0:59:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它们让我怀念往事\N{\rEnglish}but it makes me nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.16,0:59:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怀念爸爸吗  -他的钱\N{\rEnglish}- For Dad? - His money.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.32,0:59:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少你得到了一半\N{\rEnglish}Well, at least you got half.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.20,0:59:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道他怎么做到的\N{\rEnglish}I don't know how he did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.31,0:59:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白手起家建立这家公司\N{\rEnglish}building this company from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.72,0:59:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他从不回家  就是这么做到的\N{\rEnglish}He never came home. That's how he did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.60,0:59:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做这些干吗\N{\rEnglish}Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.80,0:59:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着他表扬你"干得好"吗\N{\rEnglish}Are you waiting for him to say, "Good job"?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.60,0:59:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你爸是绝不会说这话的\N{\rEnglish}'Cause your father is never gonna give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.48,0:59:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么\N{\rEnglish}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.35,0:59:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnSTKaiti\fs18}火兰德
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.80,0:59:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.96,0:59:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸的公司刚成立那会儿\N{\rEnglish}When your father was just starting off,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.12,0:59:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不知道该起什么名字\N{\rEnglish}he couldn't think of a name for the company,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.84,0:59:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后突然有一天  你给他画了一幅画\N{\rEnglish}and then one day, you drew a picture of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.32,0:59:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他极少陪你  但他是爱你的\N{\rEnglish}He was never there, but he loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.50,0:59:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnSTKaiti\fs18}公司章程
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.68,0:59:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是你的公司\N{\rEnglish}It's your company, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.16,0:59:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给这地方起的名字\N{\rEnglish}You named the damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.80,0:59:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家公司对一个病人如此关心实属罕见\N{\rEnglish}It's rare for a company to be so interested in a patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.32,0:59:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆不仅仅是老板  他还是朋友\N{\rEnglish}Tom wasn't just a boss, he was a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.08,0:59:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道他怎么样了\N{\rEnglish}I want to know how he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.16,0:59:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能明天就会醒来  也可能永远沉睡\N{\rEnglish}He could wake up tomorrow, he could stay like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.08,0:59:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无从知晓\N{\rEnglish}We really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.28,0:59:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那概率有多大呢  -很难说\N{\rEnglish}- Well, what are the odds? - It's hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.96,0:59:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就目前而言  小于1%\N{\rEnglish}At this point, less than 1%?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.56,0:59:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你已经做过功课了\N{\rEnglish}If you've done your research,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.58,0:59:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你还想知道什么\N{\rEnglish}I don't know what else you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.60,1:00:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心你给了他妻子错误的希望\N{\rEnglish}I'm concerned that you're giving his wife false hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.52,1:00:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉她了我们不能确定\N{\rEnglish}I told her we don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.88,1:00:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道  这么说会让人觉得有其他可能\N{\rEnglish}Well, you know, that makes it sound like it could go either way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.52,1:00:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能左右她的决定\N{\rEnglish}I can't tell her what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.56,1:00:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望你告诉她真相\N{\rEnglish}I just want you to tell her the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.08,1:00:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖延时间对这个家庭太残忍了\N{\rEnglish}Dragging this out is so hard on this family.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.20,1:00:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你好好想想\N{\rEnglish}Just think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.56,1:00:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉  你真迷人\N{\rEnglish}Lara, you're so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.88,1:00:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有经常赞美你吗\N{\rEnglish}Did I tell you often enough?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.24,1:01:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想说\N{\rEnglish}I just wanna say that I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.08,1:01:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\rEnglish}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.12,1:01:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来\N{\rEnglish}Hello, there. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.48,1:01:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚没心情陪你疯\N{\rEnglish}I'm not in the mood for crazy tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.76,1:01:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子\N{\rEnglish}Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.72,1:01:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜这对你来说也不容易吧  毛绒裤先生\N{\rEnglish}I guess this isn't easy for you, huh, Mr. Fuzzypants?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.12,1:01:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇见这样的家庭\N{\rEnglish}Meeting a family like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.60,1:01:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要抱抱吗\N{\rEnglish}Do you need a cuddle?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.32,1:01:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚有人需要抱抱吗\N{\rEnglish}Somebody need a cuddle tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.12,1:01:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.28,1:01:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只属于咱俩的特别享受哦\N{\rEnglish}This is a special treat just for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.60,1:01:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说出去了\N{\rEnglish}Don't tell.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.68,1:01:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲催的是  我无人可说\N{\rEnglish}Sadly, I've got no one to tell.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.12,1:01:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉如何\N{\rEnglish}How does that feel, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.16,1:01:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常难过\N{\rEnglish}Very, very sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.52,1:01:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安\N{\rEnglish}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.72,1:01:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\rEnglish}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.48,1:01:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉\N{\rEnglish}Lara.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.08,1:02:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉  醒醒\N{\rEnglish}Lara, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.32,1:02:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想当我的发型师吗\N{\rEnglish}Are you trying to be my hairdresser?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.88,1:02:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\rEnglish}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.56,1:02:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他上来\N{\rEnglish}Send him right up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.88,1:02:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来卖公司的吗\N{\rEnglish}Do you have a company to sell?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.20,1:02:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  大楼开幕仪式今晚举行\N{\rEnglish}No, the tower opening's tonight
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.48,1:02:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没在名单上看见你的名字\N{\rEnglish}and I didn't see your name on the list.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.64,1:02:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太喜欢抛头露面\N{\rEnglish}I'm not getting out much.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.48,1:02:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能来我们荣幸之至\N{\rEnglish}We'd love to have you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.56,1:02:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们当然会了\N{\rEnglish}I'm sure you would.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.16,1:02:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉  我们都很想念汤姆\N{\rEnglish}Lara, we all miss Tom very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.92,1:02:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我没有立场说这话  但你得知道\N{\rEnglish}And maybe it's not my place to say this, but you have to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.96,1:02:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他不会醒来了  -妈妈\N{\rEnglish}- He's not coming back. - Mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.32,1:02:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回你的房间  丽贝卡\N{\rEnglish}Go back to your room, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.76,1:02:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在说什么\N{\rEnglish}What is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.20,1:02:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾一下准备去上学了好吗  甜心\N{\rEnglish}Just get ready for school, okay, sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.36,1:02:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说些什么\N{\rEnglish}You don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.72,1:02:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生们说他还有机会\N{\rEnglish}The doctors say he has a chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.08,1:02:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解  如果我是你\N{\rEnglish}I understand. If I were you,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.64,1:02:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会不惜一切代价让他活下来\N{\rEnglish}I would do anything to keep him alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.40,1:02:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-但他可能会昏迷好几个月  -我可以等\N{\rEnglish}- But this could go on for months. - I can wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.40,1:03:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者数年  甚至永远都醒不过来\N{\rEnglish}Or years. And he never wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.68,1:03:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽贝卡  她需要哀悼父亲\N{\rEnglish}And Rebecca, she needs to mourn,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.20,1:03:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可如果她一直等待永远不会回来的父亲\N{\rEnglish}she can't do that if she's waiting
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.56,1:03:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她也永远尽不了孝了\N{\rEnglish}for a father who's never coming home.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.04,1:03:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩  不要\N{\rEnglish}Ian, don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.24,1:03:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\rEnglish}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.04,1:03:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把它弄走\N{\rEnglish}Get this off of me!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.96,1:03:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  把这畜生弄走\N{\rEnglish}Please! Get this beast off of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.20,1:03:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  进笼子里去\N{\rEnglish}All right, in the cage.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.32,1:03:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做错什么了\N{\rEnglish}What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.40,1:03:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要进笼子里去\N{\rEnglish}You are going into the cage.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.76,1:03:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是个野猫  你得把它送去动物收容所\N{\rEnglish}That cat is feral, and you need to take it to the pound.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.64,1:03:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是新西服\N{\rEnglish}This is a brand new suit!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.52,1:03:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算它不挠你  我也会亲自动手\N{\rEnglish}He just clawed you before I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.56,1:03:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-劳拉  -我可不是傻瓜\N{\rEnglish}- Lara... - I am not an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.44,1:03:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这可不是因为关心我\N{\rEnglish}You're not here because you care about me
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.12,1:03:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽贝卡或者汤姆\N{\rEnglish}or about Rebecca or about Tom.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.56,1:03:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会拔掉我丈夫的供氧插头来助纣为虐\N{\rEnglish}And I am not unplugging my husband to help your bottom line.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.52,1:03:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  妈妈\N{\rEnglish}Bye, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.54,1:03:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等亲爱的  我送你去学校\N{\rEnglish}Wait, honey, I'll walk you to school.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.56,1:03:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  妈妈\N{\rEnglish}No, it's okay, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.84,1:03:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几个街区而已  我已经11岁了\N{\rEnglish}It's only a couple of blocks and I'm 11.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.76,1:03:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.72,1:04:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂  你想保护丽贝卡\N{\rEnglish}I understand. You want to protect Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.84,1:04:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我想保护公司\N{\rEnglish}And I want to protect the company.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.08,1:04:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们都需要同一样东西\N{\rEnglish}But we both need the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.12,1:04:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不送  伊恩\N{\rEnglish}Goodbye, Ian.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.00,1:04:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干洗好的衣服呢\N{\rEnglish}Where's my dry cleaning?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.48,1:04:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考克斯先生  你该上塔了\N{\rEnglish}Mr. Cox, you're scheduled at the tower.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.04,1:04:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  告诉董事会我迟点到\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, I know. Tell the Board I'm running late.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.32,1:04:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他们都在布兰德先生的办公室  -什么\N{\rEnglish}- Oh, they're in Mr. Brand's office. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.52,1:04:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我把你和活动策划人的会面时间提前了\N{\rEnglish}But I moved up your meeting with the event planner.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.32,1:04:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是应该在大楼里吗\N{\rEnglish}Why aren't you at the tower?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.56,1:04:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你说要开会  -我没说\N{\rEnglish}- You called a meeting. - I didn't call a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.12,1:04:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大卫召集的会议\N{\rEnglish}David called the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.76,1:04:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算通知我的吗\N{\rEnglish}Were you gonna tell me?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.88,1:04:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说他只需要董事会成员\N{\rEnglish}He said he just needed the Board.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.85,1:04:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnSTKaiti\fs18}猫的神秘论
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.96,1:04:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想明白了\N{\rEnglish}You figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.64,1:05:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,董事会成员在哪里\N{\rEnglish}Where's the Board?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.72,1:05:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让他们去大厦了\N{\rEnglish}I sent them ahead to the tower.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.20,1:05:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉他们错过了你的会议\N{\rEnglish}Sorry they missed your meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.36,1:05:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我们去那里开吧\N{\rEnglish}That's okay. We'll do it there.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.56,1:05:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会进行一次投票\N{\rEnglish}We're gonna have a little vote.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.72,1:05:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  你知道吗  你不会参加开幕式\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, you know, you're not going to the opening.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.20,1:05:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真的吗  -没错  布兰德先生不再为我们工作了\N{\rEnglish}- Really? - Yeah. Mr. Brand no longer works for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.72,1:05:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说得对  这个公司是我的\N{\rEnglish}He's right. I own the company.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.24,1:05:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是  请把他护送出去\N{\rEnglish}Not yet. Please escort him off the property.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.20,1:05:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我\N{\rEnglish}Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.28,1:05:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩  你这样做  我会带着一队律师来找你的\N{\rEnglish}Ian, you do this, I will come at you with an army of lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.04,1:05:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请便  告我啊\N{\rEnglish}Go ahead. Sue me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.40,1:05:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等明天我们都有钱了再告\N{\rEnglish}Do it tomorrow when we're both rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.08,1:05:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的以为用几个保镖\N{\rEnglish}Do you really think you can
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.05,1:05:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能占有火兰德吗\N{\rEnglish}steal FireBrand with a couple of bouncers?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.64,1:05:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得你父亲的一张条子就能阻止我吗\N{\rEnglish}And you think you can stop me with a note from Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.52,1:05:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲就要死了  你丢掉了他的公司\N{\rEnglish}Your father's dying. You lost his company.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.28,1:05:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后  你也成不了汤姆·布兰德\N{\rEnglish}At the end of the day, you're not Tom Brand.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.36,1:05:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnSTKaiti\fs18}喵金斯宠物店
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.52,1:05:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看谁回来了\N{\rEnglish}Look who's back.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.00,1:05:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会回来的\N{\rEnglish}I knew you'd be back.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.76,1:05:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看谁来了\N{\rEnglish}Look who's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.48,1:06:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能为你做什么  小寿星\N{\rEnglish}What can I do for you, birthday girl?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.48,1:06:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要你收回这只猫\N{\rEnglish}I want you to take the cat back.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.24,1:06:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他做什么了\N{\rEnglish}What's he done?
